nz.org.p2p.model.member.authentication.api
Interface PasswordResetTokenService

public interface PasswordResetTokenService

The IPasswordResetToken interface encapsulates token information for password re-authorisation.

Author:
John Hutcheson

Method Detail

getAccessCode

java.lang.String getAccessCode()
Gets the access code, a code that can be used to frustrate bots.

Returns:
the access code - short random string bots can't guess. Users should be able to supply this value after having received it via alternative media. An MD5 hash of this value can be used to Validate it on the client or by the server.
